-- FADO IRISH PUB (BUCKHEAD) -- Liverpool OLSC Atlanta Home
-- ============================================================
UPDATE bars SET content = '<h3>The Vibe</h3>
<p>Fado Buckhead is the grander, more expansive sibling to its Midtown counterpart, occupying a three-story building on Buckhead Avenue that includes multiple dining rooms and several rooftop patios. But on Premier League Saturday mornings, none of that matters except the screens and the scarves. This is the official home of OLSC Atlanta, the Official Liverpool Supporters Club, and when the Reds are playing, the pub belongs to them.</p>

<h3>The Liverpool Connection</h3>
<p>OLSC Atlanta is one of the larger Official Liverpool Supporters Clubs in the American South. They meet at Fado Buckhead for every Liverpool match, creating a sea of red in one of Atlanta''s most upscale neighborhoods. The group maintains an active presence on social media and runs events throughout the season. Their tagline, "Y''all Never Walk Alone," perfectly captures the blend of Liverpool tradition and Southern hospitality.</p>

<h3>The Setup</h3>
<p>The three-story layout means there is always room to spread out, and the rooftop patios offer a unique viewing experience on nice days. Like the Midtown location, the interior was designed and constructed in Ireland with authentic materials, deep woods, and traditional fixtures. Multiple screens on every level ensure you can follow the match from anywhere in the building. The Buckhead location tends to be slightly quieter than Midtown on non-Liverpool match days, making it a more relaxed option for a morning EPL session.</p>

<h3>Food and Drink</h3>
<p>The menu mirrors the Midtown location -- proper Irish pub food, a strong whiskey collection, and a well-poured pint of Guinness. Weekend brunch service is popular with the post-match crowd. The rooftop bar serves a full menu and is a destination in its own right during warm weather.</p>

<h3>Getting There</h3>
<p>Located in the heart of Buckhead Village, the pub is easily accessible from GA-400 and within walking distance of the Buckhead MARTA station. The pub validates parking for 3 hours at nearby Buckhead Village parking decks, which is a significant perk in one of Atlanta''s priciest parking neighborhoods.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'fado-irish-pub-buckhead-atlanta';

